RHMessageBubble

Version 1.0
22. August 2011
Author: Ralph Harrer
Web: http://www.ralphharrer.at
Project website: http://development.ralphharrer.at/ios/RHMessageBubble/


INSTRUCTIONS
------------
Import the following files into your project:
Source/RHMessageBubble.h
Source/RHMessageBubble.m

Start displaying messages with the methods defined in
Source/RHMessageBubble.h

The message bubbles will remove themselves if you specify a time in the "forSeconds" parameter.
Otherwise you need to remove them manually by calling
[RHMessageBubble removeBubbleFromView:view];


EXAMPLES
--------
[RHMessageBubble bubbleWithSpinnerAndString:@"Hello World" toView:self.view forSeconds:2.0f];

or
[RHMessageBubble bubbleWithSpinnerAndString:@"Hello World" toView:self.view];
...
[RHMessageBubble removeBubbleFromView:self.view];
					
					
For further examples check out the demo project